952
00:34:32,020 --> 00:34:33,410
乐意之至
I'd like that very much.

953
00:34:34,340 --> 00:34:35,390
那就好好待他们
Treat them well.

954
00:34:36,720 --> 00:34:37,680
我会的
I will.

955
00:34:55,120 --> 00:34:56,200
