and you're letting them get away with it.

996
00:37:02,460 --> 00:37:04,580
我是他们的律师  不是检察官
I'm their lawyer. I'm not a prosecutor.

997
00:37:05,090 --> 00:37:07,050
亚历克斯・威廉姆斯到底有你什么把柄
What the fu-- does Alex Williams have on you, huh?

998
00:37:07,050 --> 00:37:08,210
