What are you doing here?

1061
00:39:57,450 --> 00:39:58,860
有些话要跟你说清楚
I'm here to come clean to you.

1062
00:39:58,900 --> 00:40:00,000
哈维知道你过来吗
Does Harvey know you're here?

1063
00:40:00,000 --> 00:40:02,140
不知道  事实上他叫我不要找你
No--in fact, he told me not to talk to you at all,

1064
00:40:02,140 --> 00:40:04,000
但你有权知道真相...
but you have a right to know the truth, and...

1065
00:40:05,030 --> 00:40:07,260
我已经厌烦被这件事威胁了
I'm tired of having this whole thing hanging over my head.

1066
00:40:08,820 --> 00:40:09,760
进来说吧
Come on in.

1067
00:40:16,940 --> 00:40:19,320
亚历克斯告诉布莱顿我不去了之后
After Alex told Bratton that I wasn't coming,

1068
00:40:19,610 --> 00:40:20,460
公司把他贬的一无是处
he was nothing.

1069
00:40:20,460 --> 00:40:22,270
交给他毫无胜算的案子
They gave him unwinnable cases

1070
00:40:22,270 --> 00:40:24,080
还让他每天工作10小时以上
and worked him 90 hours a week

1071
00:40:24,080 --> 00:40:25,730
直到有一天  布莱顿告诉他
until one day, Bratton came to him

1072
00:40:25,730 --> 00:40:27,700
有一个办法挽回
and said there was a way back.

1073
00:40:27,960 --> 00:40:28,940
他需要做的就是
All he had to do was take on

1074
00:40:28,940 --> 00:40:30,910
接下马斯特森建筑公司的委托
Masterson Construction as a client.

1075
00:40:30,910 --> 00:40:32,580
-是的  -他答应了
- Exactly. - And he said yes.

1076
00:40:32,580 --> 00:40:33,740
我当然同意了
Of course I said yes.

1077
00:40:33,740 --> 00:40:35,310
没什么危险
There were no red flags.

1078
00:40:35,320 --> 00:40:38,180
犯人工作的弃权书只是一些生意上的事
The waiver that put inmates to work was just smart business.

1079
00:40:39,440 --> 00:40:41,120
表面上看都是合法的
On the surface, everything was legit.

1080
00:40:41,120 --> 00:40:42,610
那你是怎么发现那不合法的
So how'd you figure out it wasn't?

1081
00:40:42,610 --> 00:40:44,290
一天我在布伦斯维克监狱
One day, I was at Brunswick,

1082
00:40:44,290 --> 00:40:45,450
警卫递给我一张纸条
and a guard gave me a letter.

1083
00:40:46,030 --> 00:40:48,060
上面写着有犯人在工地上死了
It said an inmate had died on the job site,

1084
00:40:48,120 --> 00:40:49,660
但事情被挡下来了
and that it was being covered up.

1085
00:40:49,670 --> 00:40:51,910
我猜猜  你告诉了马斯特森的首席执行官
Let me guess: you took it to Pat Kreuger,

1086
00:40:51,910 --> 00:40:52,700
派特・克鲁格
Masterson's CEO,

1087
00:40:52,700 --> 00:40:55,200
他说会着手调查
and he said that he'd look into it.

1088
00:40:55,200 --> 00:40:57,290
两周后  那个警卫被犯人杀了
Two weeks later, that guard was murdered by an inmate.

1089
00:40:57,290 --> 00:40:58,240
天呐
Holy shit.

1090
00:40:58,240 --> 00:41:00,800
那时候他才知道马斯特森建筑公司
And that's when he knew Masterson and Reform Corp.

1091
00:41:00,800 --> 00:41:02,220
和改造公司一开始就密谋好了
had been colluding from the start.

1092
00:41:02,220 --> 00:41:03,100
然后他怎么做的
So what did he do?

1093
00:41:03,100 --> 00:41:04,650
他去找了管理合伙人
He went to his managing partner,

1094
00:41:04,650 --> 00:41:07,530
汤米・布莱顿说这不是两党勾结
and Tommy Bratton said it wasn't collusion between two parties.

1095
00:41:07,530 --> 00:41:09,460
而是三党勾结
It was collusion between three parties.

1096
00:41:09,460 --> 00:41:11,930
他们把我的津贴和关键日期都联系到一起
They tied all my bonuses to all the key dates...

1097
00:41:11,930 --> 00:41:13,870
-放弃书  -建筑的开始
- The waiver... - The start of construction...

1098
00:41:13,870 --> 00:41:15,000
-警卫的死  -看起来都像
- The guard's death... - It looked like

1099
00:41:15,000 --> 00:41:16,350
我精心策划的这整起事件
I orchestrated the whole damn thing.

1100
00:41:16,350 --> 00:41:17,940
所以你掩盖了谋杀的事实
So you covered up a murder?

1101
00:41:17,940 --> 00:41:19,280
我没有证据
I had no proof of anything.

1102
00:41:19,280 --> 00:41:21,350
我有妻女  而我又脱不了干系
I had a wife and daughter, and it looked like I was in on it.

1103
00:41:21,350 --> 00:41:24,030
哈维  这太可怕了  但与你无关
Harvey, that's horrible, but this isn't on you.

1104
00:41:24,630 --> 00:41:26,760
亚历克斯可以打匿名举报电话啊
Alex still could've made a call anonymously.

1105
00:41:26,760 --> 00:41:29,340
如果你发现迈克是个骗子你也会打的
And so could you when you found out Mike was a fraud.

1106
00:41:29,920 --> 00:41:32,050
你不是罪犯  但你的手也不干净了
You didn't have to be a party to a crime, but you were.

1107
00:41:32,050 --> 00:41:33,070
他的罪不是谋杀
That crime wasn't a murder.

1108
00:41:33,070 --> 00:41:35,140
你听我说了吗  唐娜  他们有他的把柄
Did you hear me, Donna? They had him.

1109
00:41:35,140 --> 00:41:37,050
我有妻子有女儿  而他们陷害我
I had a wife and daughter, and they set me up.

1110
00:41:37,050 --> 00:41:38,260
我能怎么办
What was I supposed to do?

1111
00:41:40,110 --> 00:41:42,290
迈克  我恨这些人
Mike, I hate these people.

1112
00:41:42,290 --> 00:41:44,180
他们就该下地狱
They deserve to go away for what they did,

1113
00:41:44,180 --> 00:41:46,240
我日日夜夜都希望
and every morning when I woke up and every night

1114
00:41:46,240 --> 00:41:48,810
让他们从世界上消失
when I went to sleep, I wanted to make that happen,

1115
00:41:48,810 --> 00:41:51,360
但我没有  原因只有一个
but I didn't, for one reason:

1116
00:41:52,540 --> 00:41:54,770
我不想让女儿失去父亲
I didn't want my daughter to grow up without a father,

1117
00:41:54,770 --> 00:41:55,730
如果你还穷追不舍的话
and if you pursue this,

1118
00:41:55,730 --> 00:41:57,530
我没有办法不卷入这场阴谋
there's no way I don't get caught up in it.

1119
00:41:57,530 --> 00:41:58,850
-你并不确定  -不  我确定
- You don't know that. - Yes, I do.

1120
00:41:58,850 --> 00:42:00,500
布莱顿不放过我们的客户
When Bratton came after our clients,

1121
00:42:00,680 --> 00:42:04,080
亚历克斯签下声明揽下全责
Alex signed a declaration saying he took full responsibility.

1122
00:42:04,080 --> 00:42:06,280
哈维  如果你想让迈克就这么过去
Harvey, if you're asking Mike to let this thing go...

1123
00:42:06,280 --> 00:42:07,600
我不知道我能不能做到
I don't know if I can do that.

1124
00:42:07,830 --> 00:42:09,440
我没有让你放下
I'm not asking you to let it go.

1125
00:42:09,480 --> 00:42:11,420
而是告诉你如果你不放下会发生什么
I'm telling you what will happen if you don't.

